Text: Rice University Cc We will get the financial details necessary to continue with the Rice proposal on Tuesday afternoon Traci has set up a meeting with Wil Uecker Associate Dean for Executive Education Jones School on Tuesday morning where we will be discussing the schools systems and streaming needs We should have a better idea after the meeting on what their needs will be in order to generate some numbers for you Robert Hoodis will be accompanying us during this meeting He will help us assess the cost of epowering the university and give us some suggestions on how we can extract the necessary revenue out of the deal Any questions please call Traci at or me at Regards Jaime E Gualy Enron Broadband Services Inc Phone Cell
